---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ButtonLink from '../components/ButtonLink.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="CV" description="朱成毅 / Max Zhu 的在线简历：教育、科研、项目、技能和课程。">
  <section class="container page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">CV</p>
    <h1>在线简历</h1>
    <p>这里是简历的网页版本；PDF 版本可放在 public/resume.pdf，并通过下方按钮下载。</p>
    <div class="button-row">
      <ButtonLink href="/resume.pdf" download>Download PDF</ButtonLink>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container page-grid">
    <aside class="side-note">Email: 12313231@mail.sustech.edu.cn<br />GitHub: github.com/zceeeeee</aside>
    <div>
      <section class="page-section">
        <SectionHeading title="Education" />
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>南方科技大学</h3>
          <p>电子系，光电信息与技术方向，2027 届本科生。</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="page-section">
        <SectionHeading title="Research Experience" />
        <div class="grid grid-2">
          <div class="info-block">
            <h3>SAW-AlN 换能器仿真与测试</h3>
            <p>声表面波器件、AlN 换能器、COMSOL 仿真与测试分析。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="info-block">
            <h3>QLED / OLED / QD 发光器件制备与表征测试</h3>
            <p>发光器件制备、材料 / 器件表征与实验数据分析。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="page-section">
        <SectionHeading title="Project Experience" />
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>代表项目</h3>
          <p>Maxicam2 视觉模块、SAW-AlN 换能器仿真与测试、嘉立创杯 / 电子设计竞赛项目。具体时间、技术栈、个人贡献和结果展示可后续补充。</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="page-section">
        <SectionHeading title="Skills" />
        <div class="grid grid-3">
          <div class="info-block">
            <h3>Programming</h3>
            <p>Python、Java、MATLAB、LaTeX</p>
          </div>
          <div class="info-block">
            <h3>Tools</h3>
            <p>Git、Linux、VS Code、Docker、Jupyter Notebook、COMSOL</p>
          </div>
          <div class="info-block">
            <h3>Domains</h3>
            <p>光电子器件、器件仿真与表征测试、信号处理、单片机 / 嵌入式系统、光学基础。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="page-section">
        <SectionHeading title="Selected Coursework" />
        <ul>
          <li>数字电子技术、模拟电子技术、固态电子学</li>
          <li>半导体光学、液晶光电子学、激光原理</li>
          <li>机器人运动与控制方法</li>
          <li>Python、MATLAB、数据处理与仿真</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
